<br />
<br />Always check the docs, the CC65 kit has a lot of features.
<br />
<br />BTW that is a very cool NES emulator/porting thing.  If anyone writes an NES game and wants to port it with this, I can supply a TG16 card (takes a surface-mount ROM in PLCC package).  I designed it a while back, I would need to order more at this point, but would be happy re-order them if it can help someone.</div>

